{"tid":60491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日第一堂學車有好多問題請教","createTime":"2016-12-30T13:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T00:54:18.000Z","uid":65404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"457d95d64b8d1b4877bc7baa968b86149a7fca26","tid":60491,"uid":65404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"棍波van 仔 有冇正確開車停車步驟<br />\n屌個師傅都唔撚睇我做既動作 掛住做自己野 都唔知岩定錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n停車應該踩brake定極力子先 我踩brake先就死左火<br />\n之後我踩哂極力子 再踩brake 就冇事 但係好似錯 個師傅又冇出聲"},{"pid":"bc14086b1dffef4a832991926f3d2d74dfaf3bc7","tid":60491,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"換師傅<br />\n個師傅睇來hea教"},{"pid":"3de405900e86dc8a8cf06dfd333a6da4d76e7f15","tid":60491,"uid":64411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"brake 減速 停車前屌clutch 再 brake"},{"pid":"9d2c21cae474973eb3bc5bcf521054091643613f","tid":60491,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"極力子 1波 地板油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3603a38b2da3b4c59d0755bc01705f328699f177","tid":60491,"uid":29236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"極力子先<br />\n但唔可以用黎滑行"},{"pid":"9d685d5ea410c9b64335add9f5a3f583d8981670","tid":60491,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"一齊踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703245b0b59bdf68b72aafd5d432a47c8a347366","tid":60491,"uid":65404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講埋開車<br />\n踩極力子 入一波 鬆手制 慢慢鬆極力子？"},{"pid":"e5982fac622633e64a45bd96f62c5bf9d34617cd","tid":60491,"uid":51499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人可分享開車前有咩步驟要做 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前學車個師傅講 有開車七步曲 不過唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc85ee846fd18e0409774b09180c3b1e1cdf69a","tid":60491,"uid":23958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人可分享開車前有咩步驟要做 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前學車個師傅講 有開車七步曲 不過唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撻匙 開燈 踩查力子入一波 吊磨擦點 望鏡同盲點 放手制 走人"},{"pid":"2919767823c7ced27899e68e367964eb4767421e","tid":60491,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"開<br />\n踩盡極子子，入一波，慢慢起極力搵摩擦點（架車會打尿震咁就係）鬆手制慢慢鬆哂極力<br />\n<br />\n停<br />\n快就踩少少break 再踩極力+踩盡break,拉手制空波"},{"pid":"2b10d14e8d94d3f4b3148a8f50743ea7007be617","tid":60491,"uid":65404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"屌 點解個師傅話就咁吊起極力子就得 都冇搵過咩摩擦點"},{"pid":"a7e1dd5f723779b7fa379eb7b789375101fa97e6","tid":60491,"uid":23958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 點解個師傅話就咁吊起極力子就得 都冇搵過咩摩擦點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吊要練 放太多會死火 踩太多會溜車"},{"pid":"761ef2fde30827118e9b80476435ed39d75b23ad","tid":60491,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"break 拖低波 差唔多停就極力子"},{"pid":"2ef7e94dccadb89e1821cb5c4724866f6e5da6c8","tid":60491,"uid":65404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"我鬆左手制先再鬆極力子 睇來做錯哂 我屌"},{"pid":"e2ca5c18fe8f31fef2bc9747cac1322f835d289e","tid":60491,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人可分享開車前有咩步驟要做 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前學車個師傅講 有開車七步曲 不過唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估係<br />\n開車前咪睇下倒後鏡，右左兩邊鏡，打燈<br />\n踩迫力，<br />\n踩極力子，<br />\n入1波，<br />\n鬆極力子、比油、鬆手掣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：有十幾年揸自動波經驗"},{"pid":"ae3da0d3d5f154d82e4d57a39dbff016b3d4fe14","tid":60491,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 點解個師傅話就咁吊起極力子就得 都冇搵過咩摩擦點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吊好簡單架咋，不過你師傅聽落靠唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd27029d1c0fd2ed4da3bb803b6706fd99d7c62","tid":60491,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"&gt;&gt;&gt;停車應該踩brake定極力子先 <br />\n輕力brake再踏盡離合器<br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt;我踩brake先就死左火<br />\n你踏得太大力會feel到部車好震，差唔多死火，輕輕力就夠<br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt;之後我踩哂極力子 再踩brake 就冇事 但係好似錯 個師傅又冇出聲<br />\n你踏曬離合器的話，除非你好快踩實個brake，如果唔係好易溜後<br />\n上斜停車可以咁做，都係果句你個brake要快踩，唔係溜後即肥<br />\n平路就先輕力brake加踩盡離合器<br />\n<br />\n有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0b5f0e3bbd4f8ca6ecb93996a992789ff2c108","tid":60491,"uid":65404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"上多堂睇下點先 咩都都冇講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25c15e231feb1d182c14c00c5df7c7d97359db8","tid":60491,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:53:26.000Z","msg":"停車: 先brake 減速 減到咁上下踩clutch 轉一波 吊住clutch咁行 岩位就慢慢放clutch踩brake 拉手制"},{"pid":"87e494151c115135af74ac6a2e92eb394d89a4c1","tid":60491,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>停車: 先brake 減速 減到咁上下踩clutch 轉一波 吊住clutch咁行 岩位就慢慢放clutch踩brake 拉手制</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e23baf9d8f76ccb4132a54f0a0df04733bb7fe0","tid":60491,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>停車: 先brake 減速 減到咁上下踩clutch 轉一波 吊住clutch咁行 岩位就慢慢放clutch踩brake 拉手制</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2波3停都可以停車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3622dff14dd605fd2c0936db0ca3c8e6fa8b9c64","tid":60491,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>停車: 先brake 減速 減到咁上下踩clutch 轉一波 吊住clutch咁行 岩位就慢慢放clutch踩brake 拉手制</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2波3波都可以停車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c2fce54e7931a8b0e78a42f0773e38d3b489237","tid":60491,"uid":46785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"我第一堂同你情況一鳩樣，打算轉師傅<br />\n點知第二堂精神哂，最後1 take pass埋<br />\n諗番好彩冇轉師傅"},{"pid":"26ec2fbfa84913b3274508584f3abcaca58ec8d8","tid":60491,"uid":46785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"第一堂你都唔會開得快啦，估你都係10km/h<br />\n你直頭可以極力子同break一齊踩"},{"pid":"0e8d4d42ddddcc7ca3e505dea0a2846b419752f8","tid":60491,"uid":67752,"like":0,"dislike":